This is the sniffjoke package

SniffJoke is a software amied to avoiding sniffing, injecting valid (but unexpected) packets in the connections.
client and server doesn't notify those packets, but a sniffer could read these and screw up in tcp flow reassembly.

official home page: http://www.delirandom.net/sniffjoke

vecna and evilaliv3 are currently developing in order to bring the 0.3 release at an almost stable and useful 0.4/1.0
